<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[القهقور]</span>: الحجر.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>... فَعْلَلى، بالفتح<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
